				h1.articleheading.kx-backgroundcolor who is KNOX?
				p.articletext Knox watched his father gasp for air in his last breaths. The seething boy genius was visibly disturbed by what lay before him but did not move, anxiously tapping his fingers on the wall. As his father's eyes closed, the child peered down onto his father's limp body and spat in his face. In the husk of his hollow family lineage, KNOX discovered a terrible purpose - the boy genius must become the boy warlord! 

				p.articletext Inheriting his father's empire of organized crime, KNOX has used his vast fortune and arsenal of weapons to live out his greedy dreams. KNOX's team of henchmen and hired help have become infamously known as the Villain Underground after a number of violent criminal incidents. Even alone, KNOX should not be underestimated. His high-tech powersuit contains a number of deadly implements while his obsessive drive for power has led many heroes and villains to an early grave.
		.row.articlerow
