						h4.articleskilltext Some Utilities in your deck are MINIONS. Whenever you would take damage, you may destroy one of your MINIONS instead.

				p.articletext So how does MINION work? Some Utilities in your deck have the MINION skill. When a Utility with MINION is in play, you may destroy that card to prevent one instance of damage dealt to you directly. By playing Utilities with MINION, Knox can avoid big chunks of damage without relying on other methods stay in the game. You can even get rid of multiple MINIONS in one turn if you find yourself under attack! 

