				p.articletext Cannon Fodder and Moronic Gangster are two Utilities from KNOX's deck with the MINION skill. That means whenever you have one of these cards in play, you can destroy them to block damage dealt to you directly. Since MINIONS only prevent individual instances of damage, it's a good idea to have multiple MINIONS in play to keep yourself safe.

